data.description: This beautiful golf course homes features 4 bedrooms 3 baths with a tray ceiling in the great room, Rinnai hot water heater, in ground pool, irrigation system on a well, utility room with a full bath, outdoor storage shed and a walk in safe in the double garage that will store your guns and or valuables, plantation shutters and ice maker that may stay with the house. This house has many other features that you just need to see.
